<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<main class="flex-1 px-6 md:px-12 py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-fg-muted text-sm mb-8">Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', {year:'numeric', month:'long', day:'numeric'}) %></p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">Jude Harper is a brand operated by <strong>Tawzer LLC</strong>. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit judeharper.com and purchase our products.</p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-2"><strong>When you make a purchase:</strong></p>
    <ul class="text-fg-secondary mb-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Name and email address</li>
      <li>Shipping address (for physical orders)</li>
      <li>Payment information (processed securely by Stripe — we never store card details)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-2"><strong>When you subscribe to our newsletter:</strong></p>
    <ul class="text-fg-secondary mb-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Email address and optional name</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-2"><strong>Automatically collected:</strong></p>
    <ul class="text-fg-secondary mb-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Basic analytics (page views, device type) via hosting provider</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="text-fg-secondary mb-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>To fulfill and deliver your orders (digital downloads and physical shipments)</li>
      <li>To send order confirmations and shipping updates</li>
      <li>To send newsletter updates (only if you subscribed)</li>
      <li>To improve our website and products</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">We use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul class="text-fg-secondary mb-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — Payment processing (PCI-DSS compliant)</li>
      <li><strong>Lulu</strong> — Print-on-demand fulfillment for physical books</li>
      <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — Secure database hosting</li>
      <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — Website hosting</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">We retain your order data for accounting and legal purposes. You may request deletion of your personal data at any time by contacting us.</p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">If you are in the EU/EEA, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul class="text-fg-secondary mb-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>Access your personal data</li>
      <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
      <li>Data portability</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">To exercise these rights, contact us at <strong>hello@judeharper.com</strong>.</p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">7. Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">We use essential cookies only (session management for admin login). We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">8. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-fg-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">Tawzer LLC<br>Email: hello@judeharper.com</p>
  </div>
</main>

